Package ext2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataBlock
    Name: DataBlock This class represents any data block which contains a sequence of bytes in the volume the user opened.
    Directory
    Name: Directory This class represents a directory in a given volume.
    Driver
    Name: Driver This class allows the user to open several files that are contained within the given volume they provide.
    Ext2File
    Title: Ext2File This class represents a file within a given volume.
    Ext2Reader
    Title: Ext2Reader This class provides an implmentation of a custom GUI to read information from a given volume.
    GroupDescriptor
    Name: GroupDescriptor This class represents a group descriptor in the file system.
    Helper
    Name: Helper This class provides methods for outputting various file system information.
    INode
    Name: iNode This class represents an iNode in the filesystem.
    SuperBlock
    Name: SuperBlock This class represents the super block in the file system.
    Volume
    Name: Volume This class represents a volume the user wishes to open and read from.
